    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't know if a therapist can fix the fact that i'm fundamentally broken. sometimes i sit there and think... if i wasn't even here, the house would be quieter, there'd be less tension, they could just have a normal, happy life without my constant chaos. it almost feels like the only selfless thing i could do is just stop being a burden to them.",
